Media
Light novel
Written by Kōshi Tachibana and illustrated by Tsunako, the first ''King's Proposal''s volume was released by Fujimi Shobo's Fujimi Fantasia Bunko imprint on September 18, 2021. As of August 2025, eight volumes have been released.
In April 2022, Yen Press announced that they had licensed the light novels; the first novel was released on November 22 of the same year.
